<h1>About the Project</h1>
<p class="subheading">The Akron City Health Dashboard is a tool that was developed through a partnership between Launch League and the city of Akron. The Akron City Health Dashboard aims to help inform  citizens of the overall &ldquo;health&rdquo; of the city and the status of different metrics recorded by city offices. </p>
<div class="content-container-2-up">
  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>History</h2>
    <p>When Mayor Dan Horrigan was elected as mayor of the city of Akron, he pledged to bring transparency about the status of the city of Akron to its citizens. To do this, a tool needed to be developed that could collect, display, and analyze this data in a way that was meaningful to citizens. Through development between Launch League and volunteers at HackNAkron events, a data API was developed to help make this city metric data usable and meaningful.</p>
