<div class="content-block">
  <h2>Future Goals</h2>
  <p>The goal of this project is to continue to develop and expand the API system to include all city metric data contained within each department. This will then allow citizens to get a complete picture of the overall &ldquo;health&rdquo; of the city, and open the door for developers to use the data in meaningful and unique ways.</p>
